Write a script that changes the owner to vincent and the group owner to staff for all the files and directories in the working directory. 

Changing the name of the owner to another name and the group owner to another name for all files and directories in the current directory.

note: The flag -h means the changes will apply to all the files in the directory and subdirectories
	The flag -R means the changes will apply to the directory and the subdirectories
No file name is specify therefore the changes will affect the current directory and subdirectories and fileis

command used is "chown -hR owner_new_name group_new_name ."

chown -hR vincent staff .

